# ==============================================================================
# HOW TO GET RESEND API KEY:
# ==============================================================================
# 1. Sign up at https://resend.com (FREE - 3,000 emails/month, 100/day)
# 2. Go to API Keys: https://resend.com/api-keys
# 3. Click "Create API Key"
# 4. Copy the key (starts with "re_") and paste it above
# 5. (Optional) Add your domain for custom "from" addresses
#
# Why Resend instead of Gmail SMTP?
# - Works on ALL hosting providers (Render, Vercel, Railway, etc.)
# - No port blocking issues
# - Better deliverability
# - Simple API, no SMTP configuration needed
